    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/10089696424b89655991beeffd4ebe7f.poster.avif?t=1757916885\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/10089696424b89655991beeffd4ebe7f.webm?t=1757916885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/10089696424b89655991beeffd4ebe7f.mp4?t=1757916885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《Fishing Online》</strong>的世界里，你将体验到最惬意的户外休闲生活。与你的好友，或是与来自世界各地的玩家们，一同开启愉快的钓鱼人生吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■ 垂钓之乐</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的钓鱼人生，从此开始！在钓场抛下鱼饵，与上钩的鱼儿展开一场充满乐趣的拉锯战吧！操作简单易上手，但每种鱼儿都有独特的挣扎节奏，让你体验到最真实的搏鱼快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/800ca7acde7ed2a63476e7c583d44f53.poster.avif?t=1757916885\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/800ca7acde7ed2a63476e7c583d44f53.webm?t=1757916885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/800ca7acde7ed2a63476e7c583d44f53.mp4?t=1757916885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■ 治愈系的卡通画风</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来感受这片由温馨笔触所描绘出的大自然吧。在清澈的江河湖泊中，你将会邂逅各种各样新奇又可爱的鱼儿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■ 采集与烹饪</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钓上来的鱼可以放养在私家鱼塘里，也可以做成美味的料理。烹饪所需的食材可以通过采集获得，做好的料理会为你提供有助于钓鱼的增益效果。不仅如此，你还可以亲手制作各种生活工具哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■ 在线同乐</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Fishing Online》中，你可以随时遇见好友或全球玩家，与他们一同游戏。在这片以全世界为蓝本的地图上尽情探索，与其他玩家分享游戏的点滴喜悦吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/56c454129bb1ce33feb4f67235111a5c.poster.avif?t=1757916885\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/56c454129bb1ce33feb4f67235111a5c.webm?t=1757916885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131550/extras/56c454129bb1ce33feb4f67235111a5c.mp4?t=1757916885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■ 持续的更新承诺</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是一家小型的独立游戏开发团队。但我们承诺，会永远倾听玩家的意见与创意，并坚持不懈地进行更新。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鱼类图鉴：在这里可以查看、记录你钓到的所有鱼儿，并确认自己的排名。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专属鱼塘：你可以在这里饲养各种各样的鱼儿，甚至是珍稀的观赏鱼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钓鱼大赛：参与全球玩家同台竞技的钓鱼大赛，根据排名赢取丰厚奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钓场扩建：我们正计划将钓鱼的舞台从淡水区域，进一步扩展至广阔的海洋！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协力讨伐：我们计划推出全新的团队玩法，你将可以和同伴们一起，协力挑战出现在地图上的特殊鱼种。</p>",
